===Etymology===
{{etymon|en|id=reference work|:lbor|la-new:encyclopaedīa<id:encyclopedia>|tree=1}}
{{bor+|en|la-new|encyclopēdīa, [[encyclopaedia|encyclopaedīa]]|t=general education}}, a [[univerbation|univerbated]] form of {{der|en|grc-koi|ἐγκύκλιος παιδείᾱ|t=education in the circle of arts and sciences}}, from {{der|en|grc|ἐγκύκλιος||[[circular]]}} + {{m|grc|παιδείᾱ||[[childrearing]]; [[education]]}} ([[q.v.]]). Nearly all modern English usage of the word was influenced by the scope and format of the {{der|en|fr|-}} ''{{w|Encyclopédie}}'' by  {{w|Diderot}} [[et al.]] (see quotation).

