#: {{uxa|en|I only use the library for the '''encyclopedia''', as we’ve got most other books here.}}
#: {{uxa|en|My old '''encyclopedia''' has been gathering dust on the shelf for the past decade.}}
#* {{quote-book|en
|author=Jean-Baptiste le Rond d'Alembert
|title=Encyclopédie ou Dictionnaire raisonné des sciences, des arts et des métiers
|title2=The '''Encyclopedia''' of Diderot & d'Alembert Collaborative Translation Project
|translators=Richard N. Schwab; Walter E. Rex.
|publisher2=Michigan Publishing, University of Michigan Library
|location=Paris
|location2=[[w:Ann Arbor, Michigan|Ann Arbor]]
|year=1751
|format2=Web
