|pages=1–45
|date2=April 18, 2009
|text=The '''Encyclopedia''' which we are presenting to the public is, as its title declares, the work of a society of men of letters. Were we not of their number, we might venture to affirm that they are all favorably known or worthy of being so.}}
#* {{quote-book|en
<!-- This title is in New Latin (see [[encyclopaedia#Latin]]), not English, so we don't embolden it -->
