===Etymology===
{{etymon|la|:bor|grc:ἐγκύκλιος παιδείᾱ<id:general education>|id=encyclopedia}}
Borrowed from a [[univerbation|univerbated]] form of {{der|la|grc|ἐγκύκλιος παιδείᾱ|t=education in the circle of arts and sciences}}, from {{m|grc|ἐγκύκλιος|t=circular}} + {{m|grc|παιδείᾱ|t=child-rearing, education}}. This spelling seems to have been first used by {{w|Paul Skalich}} in 1559, although the spelling ''encyclopedia'' goes back to at least 1517, with a work by {{w|Johannes Aventinus}}.

