##: {{syn|en|pound sterling<id:Q25224>|mul:GBP<id:Q25224><qq:symbol>|mul:£<id:Q25224><qq:symbol>|quid<id:Q25224><qq:slang>|nicker<id:Q25224>|sov<id:Q25224><qq:slang>}}
##* {{quote-journal|en|date=2012-11-11|author=Carole Cadwalladr|work=w:The Observer|title=Do online courses spell the end for the traditional university?|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/education/2012/nov/11/online-free-learning-end-of-university?INTCMP=SRCH|passage=For students in developing countries who can't get it any other way, or for students in the first world, who can but may choose not to. Pay thousands of '''pounds''' a year for your education? Or get it free online?}}
