#* {{quote-journal|en|passage=It is easier to get along when everyone, more or less, is getting ahead. But when the '''pie''' is shrinking, social groups are more likely to turn on each other.|author=w:Evan Thomas|url=http://www.newsweek.com/2010/12/04/the-deepest-dangers-facing-the-united-states.html|date=2010-12-04|title=Why It’s Time to Worry|work=Newsweek}}
