# {{lb|en|informal}} Something very easy; a [[piece of cake]].
#* {{quote-journal|en|year=1989|journal=PC Mag|volume=8|number=5|page=91|passage=Programmers haven't exactly been wild about certain Microsoft policies — such as the price of the OS/2 developer's kit or the fib about how ''Microsoft Windows'' code would be '''pie''' to translate to the Presentation Manager.}}
