#* {{quote-web|en|author=@_kirstenanna|site=w:Twitter|url=https://twitter.com/_kirstenanna/status/1042058731876433920|archiveurl=https://archive.ph/A3Bkr|archivedate=27 January 2024|date=18 September 2018|passage=just my luck been put in a presentation group at uni with a guy I '''pied''' on tinder last week HAHA gud}}

