===Etymology===
[[File:Elephant near ndutu.jpg|thumb|African bush elephant ({{taxfmt|Loxodonta africana|species}})]]
[[File:AmersfoortZooYoungAsianElephant.jpg|thumb|Asian elephant ({{taxfmt|Elephas maximus|species}})]]

From {{inh|en|enm|elefant}}, {{m|enm|elefaunt}}, from {{der|en|fro|elefant}}, {{m|fro|elefan}}, {{m|fro|olifant}}, re-latinized in {{der|en|frm|-}} as {{m|frm|elephant}}, from {{der|en|la|elephantus}}, from {{der|en|grc|ἐλέφᾱς}} (gen. {{m|grc|ἐλέφαντος}}). Believed to be derived from an {{der|en|afa|-}} form such as {{der|en|ber-pro|*eḷu|t=elephant}} (compare {{cog|thv|êlu}}, {{cog|taq|alu}}) or {{der|en|egy|ꜣbw|t=elephant; ivory}}. More at {{m|en|ivory}}. Replaced {{cog|enm|olifant}} (from the aforementioned {{w|Old French}} form, from {{cog|la-vul|*olifantus}}), which replaced {{cog|ang|elpend|t=elephant}}.

===Pronunciation===
