===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# {{senseid|en|Q7378}} A large [[mammal]] of the family {{taxfmt|Elephantidae|family}} in the order [[Proboscidea]], having a [[trunk]], and native to [[Africa]] and [[Asia]].
# {{lb|en|in particular}} Any member of the subfamily [[Elephantinae]] not also of the genera {{taxfmt|Mammuthus|genus}} and ''Primelephas''.
# {{lb|en|figurative}} Anything [[huge]] and [[ponderous]].
# {{lb|en|paper|printing}} {{synonym of|en|elephant paper}}.
# {{lb|en|British|childish}} {{n-g|used when counting to add length, so that each count takes about one second}}
#: {{ux|en|Let's play hide and seek. I'll count. One '''elephant''', two '''elephant''', three '''elephant'''...}}
# {{lb|en|uncountable|obsolete}} [[ivory|Ivory]].
#* {{RQ:Dryden Aeneis|passage=He sent rich gifts of '''elephant''' and gold.}}
# {{lb|en|xiangqi}} A [[xiangqi]] [[piece]] that is moved two points [[diagonally]], may not jump over intervening pieces and may not cross the river.

