#* {{quote-book|en|year=1864|author=United States War Department|title=The 1864 Field Artillery Tactics|pageurl=http://books.google.com/books?id=xiKdwlGeBPUC&pg=PA120&dq=double-file|page=120|publisher=Stackpole Books|year_published=2005|isbn=978-0-8117-0131-0
|passage=The column '''marching''' in double file, the instructor commands: {{...}}}}
