{{etymon|en|:inh|enm:Aprill|tree=1}}
From {{inh|en|enm|apprile}}, {{m|en|Aprill}}, re-Latinised from {{cog|enm|aueril}}, from {{der|en|fro|avrill}}, from {{der|en|la|Aprīlis||of the month of the goddess [[Venus]]}}, perhaps based on {{der|en|ett|𐌀𐌐𐌓𐌖}}, from {{der|en|grc|Ἀφροδίτη||Venus}}. Displaced native {{ncog|ang|ēastermōnaþ|t=April|lit=Easter month}}, see {{m|en|Eastermonth}}.

