* {{audio|en|en-us-November.ogg|a=US}}
* {{IPA|en|/nəˈvɛmbə(r)/|a=Indic}}
* {{hyphenation|en|No|vem|ber}}
* {{rhymes|en|ɛmbə(ɹ)|s=3}}

