===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*dʰegʷʰ-}}
From {{inh|en|enm|Monday}}, {{m|enm|Monenday}}, from {{inh|en|ang|mōnandæġ||day of the moon}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*mānini dag}}, a calque ({{m|la|interpretātiō germānica}}) of {{der|en|la|diēs Lūnae}}, equivalent to {{af|en|Moon|day|nocat=1}}. See also {{cog|ja|月曜日||Moon's day}}.
{{col-top|2|cog}}
Compare {{cog|sco|Monanday|t=Monday}}, {{cog|yol|Mondei|t=Monday}}, {{cog|stq|Moundai|t=Monday}}, {{cog|fy|moandei|t=Monday}}, {{cog|gsw|meintog}}, {{m|gsw|miantag}}, {{m|gsw|méntag}}, {{m|gsw|mìntàg}}, {{m|gsw|mäntag}}, {{m|gsw|Määntig|t=Monday}}, {{cog|bar|Monda}}, {{m|bar|Mondåg}}, {{m|bar|montach}}, {{m|bar|monti|t=Monday}}, {{cog|cim|matak}}, {{m|cim|menta}}, {{m|cim|méentag|t=Monday}}, {{cog|nl|maandag|t=Monday}}, {{cog|de|Montag|t=Monday}}, {{cog|nds-de|Maandag|t=Monday}}, {{cog|lb|Méindeg|t=Monday}}, {{cog|mhn|ma'ta|t=Monday}}, {{cog|pdc|Mundaag}}, {{m|pdc|Muundaag|t=Monday}}, {{cog|wym|möntaog|t=Monday}}, {{cog|vls|moandag|t=Monday}}, {{cog|yi|מאָנטיק|t=Monday}}, {{cog|da|-}}, {{cog|nb|mandag|t=Monday}}, {{cog|fo|mánadagur|t=Monday}}, {{cog|is|mánudagur|t=Monday}}, {{cog|nn|-}}, {{cog|sv|måndag|t=Monday}}, {{cog|fi|maanantai|t=Monday}}.
{{col-bottom}}

