===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{senseid|en|Q105}}The second [[day]] of the week in many religious traditions, and the first day of the [[week]] in systems using the [[w:ISO 8601|ISO 8601]] norm. It follows [[Sunday]] and precedes [[Tuesday]].
#: {{syn|en|Second Day|q=Quakerism}}
#* {{RQ:Orwell Animal Farm|6
|passage=Mr. Whymper, a solicitor living in Willingdon, {{...|had agreed to act as intermediary between Animal Farm and the outside world, and}} would visit the farm every '''Monday''' morning to receive his instructions.}}
#* {{quote-journal|en|author=Amir Vera|title=Louisville detective who fatally shot Breonna Taylor is appealing his termination from the police department|magazine=w:CNN|url=https://www.cnn.com/2021/12/13/us/myles-cosgrove-breonna-taylor-termination-appeal-hearing/index.html|date=2021-12-13|passage=An LMPD Board Notice of Hearing states part of Cosgrove’s hearings took place in November. The second half of his hearing is set to begin '''Monday''' and end Wednesday.}}

