===Alternative forms===
* {{alt|enm|wedenesday|wednesday|Wednesdei|Wedonesday}}
* {{alter|enm|weodnesdei||AB}}; {{alter|enm|wodnysday||Kent}}; {{alter|enm|wodnesdai|wodinsdai||Oxon}}
* {{alter|enm|Wennessday|Wensday|Wonnysday|wonysday||syncopic, mostly <<Late ME>>}}

===Etymology===
{{inh+|enm|ang|wōdnesdæġ}}, from {{inh|enm|gmw-pro|*Wōdanas dag}}.

Forms in {{IPAchar|/ɛ/}} likely reflect {{m|ang|*wēdnesdæġ}}, from {{inh|enm|gmw-pro|*Wōdinas dag}}; compare {{cog|dum|wenesdach}} (for usual {{m|dum|woensdach}}) and {{cog|ofs|wernisdei}}.

===Pronunciation===
