* {{IPA|en|/ˈθɝz.deɪ/|/-.di/|a=GA}} ({{enPR|thûrzˈ -dā|-dē}})
** {{audio|en|En-us-Thursday.ogg|a=GA}}
* {{IPA|en|/ˈθɘːz.dæɪ̯/|a=AU}}
