==Middle English==

===Alternative forms===
* {{alter|enm|Thoresday|Thuresday|Thurysday|Þursday}}

===Etymology===
From {{inh|enm|ang|þuresdæġ}}, {{m|ang|þursdæġ}}, late form of {{m|ang|þunresdæġ}}, from {{inh|enm|gmw-pro|*Þunras dag}}. Possibly influenced by [[Old Norse]] {{m|non|þórsdagr}}, though compare the development of early {{m+|enm|are}} from {{m|ang|ānre}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|enm|/ˈθur(i)zdæi̯/}}
* {{IPA|enm|/ˈθyːrzdæi̯/|aa=Northern}}

