===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|la-med|connotātiō}}, from {{m|la|connotō|t=to mark in addition}}, from {{der|en|la|con-|t=together, with}} + {{m|la|notō|t=to note}}; equivalent to {{suffix|en|connote|ation}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|en|/ˌkɒnəˈteɪʃən/|a=RP}}
** {{audio|en|LL-Q1860 (eng)-Vealhurl-connotation.wav|a=Southern England}}
* {{IPA|en|/ˌkɑnəˈteɪʃən/|a=GA,dialects of Canada}}
* {{IPA|en|/ˌkɒnəˈteɪʃən/|a=CA,dialects of the US}}
