===Etymology===
From {{bor|en|la-lat|dēnotātiō}}, from {{der|en|la|denoto|dēnotāre|t=to denote, mark out}} + {{m|la|-tiō|pos=suffix forming nouns of action}}, from {{m|la|dē-|t=completely}} + {{m|la|noto|notāre|t=to mark}}; equivalent to {{af|en|denote|-ation}}.

===Pronunciation===
