===Etymology===
{{etymon|en|:inh|enm:noun|tree=+|text=*|nodot=+}}, from {{der|en|xno|nom|noun, non, nom}}, from {{der|en|la|nōmen||name; noun}}. The grammatical sense in Latin was a semantic loan from {{noncog|grc-koi|ὄνομα}}. {{doublet|en|name|nomen}}.

