==English==

===Etymology===
{{etymon|en|:inh|enm:ethymologie|tree=1}}
From {{inh|en|enm|ethymologie}}, from {{der|en|fro|ethimologie}}, from {{der|en|la|etymologia}}, from {{der|en|grc|ἐτυμολογία}}, from {{m|grc|ἔτυμον||true sense}} and {{m|grc|-λογία||study or logic of}}, from {{m|grc|λόγος||word; explanation}}. Equivalent to {{af|en|etymon|-ology}}.

