===Etymology===
{{etymon|en|:inh|enm:craft|tree=1}}
{{inh+|en|enm|craft|t=strength, skill}}, from {{inh|en|ang|cræft|t=strength, skill}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*kraftu}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*kraftuz|t=strength, power}}; further origin obscure.
