# {{lb|en|intransitive}} To [[trade]] professionally (''followed by'' '''in''').
#: {{syn|en|sell|trade|bargain}}
#: {{ux|en|She '''deals''' in gold.}}
# {{lb|en|ambitransitive}} To [[sell]], especially to sell [[illicit]] [[drug]]s.
