===Etymology 2===
From {{inh|en|enm|heed}}, from {{inh|en|ang|hēafod-||main}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*haubida-}}, derived from the noun {{m|gmw-pro|*haubid||head}}. 

Cognate with {{cog|stq|hööft-}}, {{cog|fy|haad-}}, {{cog|nl|hoofd-}}, {{cog|nds-de|höövd-}}, {{cog|de|haupt-}}.

