===Etymology 1===
{{PIE word|en|h₁nómn̥}}
{{etymon|en|id=noun|:inh|enm:name|tree=1}}
From {{inh|en|enm|name}}, {{m|enm|nome}}, from {{inh|en|ang|nama}}, {{m|ang|noma}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*namō}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*namô|t=name}}, from {{inh|en|ine-pro|*h₁nómn̥|t=name}}.

{{col-top|2|cog}}
