===Etymology 5===
{{etymon|en|id=alpha-priv|:der|grc:ἀ-}}
From {{der|en|grc|ἀ-}}, [[preconsonantal]] form of {{m|grc|ἀν-}}. Distant {{dbt|en|un-|nocap=1}}.

====Pronunciation====
