===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*h₁er-|id=earth}}
{{bor+|en|af|aardvark}} {{q|obsolete}}, {{m|af|erdvark}}, from {{af|nocat=1|af|aarde|t1=earth|pos1=from {{der|en|dum|aerde}}|vark|t2=pig|pos2=from {{der|en|dum|varken}}}}. Early European colonists in South Africa noticed that the animal was similar to a pig, while ''aarde'' hints at the animal's habit of burrowing.

