===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The [[nocturnal]], [[insectivorous]], burrowing [[mammal]] {{taxfmt|Orycteropus afer|species}}, of the order {{taxfmt|Tubulidentata|order}} and somewhat resembling a [[pig]]. Common in some parts of sub-Saharan Africa. {{defdate|from late 18<sup>th</sup> c.}}
#: {{syn|en|African anteater|antbear|ant bear|anteater|earth pig}}
#: {{ux|en|The '''aardvark''' burrows in the ground and feeds mostly on termites, which it catches with its long, slimy tongue.}}
#* {{quote-journal|en|date=August 15, 2007|author=Wayne A. Davis|title=Replies to Green, Szabó, Jeshion, and Siebel|work=Philosophical Studies|url=|doi=10.1007/s11098-007-9128-6|volume=137|issue=3|pages=
|passage=If ‘'''aardvark''' lover’ has that syntactic structure, then it determinately means “lover of '''aardvarks'''.}}

